In Japan, people like to combine words and shorten words way too much. For example, here, "Hina's pussy" becomes "Hinussy". In Japan pussy is called "Manko" and the polite version would be "Omanko". Since they are siblings they don't use polite version. Hina's name ends with an "a" sound and "Manko" starts with "ma". Thus "ma" in "Manko" is replaced with "Hina" from Hina which becomes "Hinanko".
